The '''Central Storage Core''' was the large central area of ''[[Outbound Flight]]'', surrounded by six [[Dreadnaught-class heavy cruiser/Legends|''Dreadnaught''-class heavy cruisers]]. It contained the [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]] and supplies that the colonists would need on their journey, and was arranged so that if any of the six Dreadnaughts detached, they could each easily load one-sixth of its supplies into their [[Starship/Legends|ship]].<ref name="Outbound Flight">[[Outbound Flight (novel)|''Outbound Flight'']]</ref>

The only survivors of the [[Battle for Outbound Flight|attack]] that destroyed ''Outbound Flight'' and its subsequent crash into a [[Planetoid/Legends|planetoid]] in [[The Redoubt/Legends|the Redoubt]], were the crew and passengers that [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Jorus C'baoth]] imprisoned in the core.<ref name="Outbound Flight" />

